<P><B>SMALL SCHOOLS COMMITTEE</B>:</P>
<P>It shall be the purpose of the Small Schools Committee to determine the special issues and concerns that are special or of particular significance to the small school districts of Wisconsin.  The issues and subjects are to be clearly defined and recommendations for assistance from the state association developed and proposed to the WASDA Board of Directors. Suggested topics for special workshops designated for the small school districts in Wisconsin could be proposed for consideration.</P>
<OL>
