<P><B>TEACHER/PRINCIPAL OF THE YEAR COMMITTEE</B>:</P>
<P>The WASDA members on the Teacher/Principal of the Year Selection Committee are charged with representing their CESAs on a joint committee with members of other educational associations to review candidates and to make recommendations for representatives from their respective CESAs for the annual teacher and principal of the year selections.  The committee members are also responsible for promoting the teacher/principal of the year concept withintheir respective CESAs.</P>

