<LI>Larry Rush-Neosho Jt. #3</LI>
</OL>



<P><B>LIAISON WITH HIGHER EDUCATION COMMITTEE</B>:</P>
<P>The WASDA Liaison With Higher Education Committee will have three primary functions:  (1) to review and take positions on proposed changes in the teacher/administrator certification requirements; (2) to review current teacher/administrator preparation programs and recommend improvements; (3) to pursue a midcareer inservice program for Wisconsin school administrators.</P>
<OL>
