<LI>Fred Sams-Benton</LI>
</OL>



<P><B>SCHOOL FACILITIES COMMITTEE</B>:</P>
<P>This committee will serve as a watchdog committee for issues relating to school district bond referendums to replace old and inadequate buildings.  This committee may be called upon to meet when special legislative issues are being considered or when studies or reports are needed on physical conditions of public school buildings in Wisconsin.</P>
<OL>
<LI>  CHAIR:  Ken Ochalla-Omro     6. Jerry Rosso-Palmyra-Eagle</LI>
