<H3><CENTER>REPORTING ON INFERTILTY &amp; <BR>ASSISTED REPRODUCTIVE
TECHNOLOGIES</CENTER>
</H3><P><HR>
<H3>Volume 1, No. 1 Summer 1989
</H3><B>
