<!--name-->LEWIS, 
<!--misc-->Sir 
<!--name-->ARTHUR, 
<!--misc-->United 
<!--misc-->Kingdom,, 
<!--misc-->Princeton 
<!--misc-->University, 
<!--misc-->Princeton, 
<!--name-->NJ, 
<!--misc-->U.S.A., 
<!--english motivation--> "for  their pioneering  research into economic development research with particular consideration of the  problems of developing countries".
<!--misc-->
<p>
<!--misc-->
<H3>The Nobel Prize in Economic Sciences 1980</H3>
<!--misc-->
<!--name-->KLEIN, 
<!--name-->LAWRENCE 
<!--misc-->R., 
<!--misc-->U.S.A., 
<!--misc-->University 
<!--misc-->of 
<!--misc-->Pennsylvania, 
<!--misc-->Philadelphia, 
<!--name-->PA, 
<!--english motivation--> "for the creation of econometric models and the application to the analysis of economic  fluctuations and economic policies".
