Changing your Password(s).</a>

<li> Using the Suns in the lab for your 
<a href="http://www.econ.lsa.umich.edu/labdocs/email.html">
Electronic Mail.</a>

<li> Using your home directory on the file server to 
<a href="http://www.econ.lsa.umich.edu/labdocs/homedir.html">
Store DOS Files Without Floppy Disks.</a>

<li> The <a href="http://www.econ.lsa.umich.edu/labdocs/mtools.html">
mtools</a>
package, which allows you to use MS-DOS floppy disks with the Suns. 

